<p>Though it is simple, it will be very beneficial in cases which involves complex data structures like,</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"><span class="n">floatingView</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">panel</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">shouldScroll</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="nf">toggle</span><span class="p">()</span></code></pre></figure>

